href="jms-005P.xml"
title="Forester"
addr="jms-005P"
type="local">Forester</fr:link> is a tool written in the <fr:link
href="https://www.ocaml.org/"
type="external">OCaml</fr:link> programming language, and makes use of the latest features of OCaml 5. Most users should install <fr:link
href="jms-005P.xml"
title="Forester"
addr="jms-005P"
type="local">Forester</fr:link> through OCaml's <fr:link
href="https://opam.ocaml.org/"
type="external">opam</fr:link> package manager; instructions to install opam and OCaml simultaneously can be found <fr:link
href="https://opam.ocaml.org/"
type="external">here</fr:link>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
